2026-02-26T00:38:49Z | 5d8edd723c2f3d17a5e9b81e37bf6b94a0ee3d3c | Add AdminRoute guard

Implemented AdminRoute component to guard admin-only routes:
- Uses useAuth and useIsAdmin to verify authentication and admin status
- Shows a centered Loader2 while loading
- Redirects to /auth if not authenticated
- Redirects to / if not admin
- Exposes children when authorized

